===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}
{{liushu|p}} – four dots, perhaps three grains of sand (see [[沙]]), to indicate "a few, a little". Phonetically borrowed from {{och-l|小|small}}, which is depicted by three dots.

Unrelated to [[步]] (and hence [[歲]]), in which the lower component is the stylization of a foot.

